title: Bump dataclasses from 0.7 to 0.8

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

body:
Bumps [dataclasses](https://github.com/ericvsmith/dataclasses) from 0.7 to 0.8.
Commits
  • 95d2a4c Prepare for 0.8 release.
  • 75b24ef Merged changes from bpo-33796 and bpo-33805. (#140)
  • 5eee0b0 Fixed "sort order" -> "insertion order".
  • See full diff in compare view
